#   - https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/
#   - commit message structure:
#       ```
#       <type>[optional scope]: <description>
#
#       [optional body]
#
#       [optional footer(s)]
#       ```
#   - relations to semver(https://semver.org/)
#      - fix -> PATCH
#      - feat -> MINOR
#      - BREAKING CHANGE -> MAJOR
